---
title: Vegan One-Pan Corn & Bean Taco Salad with Pico de Gallo & Creamy Lime Dressing
description: This dinner idea is a study in culinary contrasts: a warm-cold, crunchy-creamy, earthy-herbal delight that will really make our Fresh Fam vegans smile. It starts with dressed salad greens and cilantro topped with warm, lightly charred corn (charring brings out the sweetness!) and black beans seasoned with savory Mexican-style spices. Top with bright pico de gallo, crumble crunchy tortilla chips over the bowl, and finish with a squeeze of lime juice for a tangy touch to this colorful 15-minute dinner salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegan-one-pan-corn-bean-taco-salad-9cefa850.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64762f872adaffbd433f8015.pdf
author: Sara Heilman
cuisine: Mexican
nutrition:
